        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Share a memory of a holiday. Where was it, who went, what happened?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>It was in my city and I was 13 years old. With a friend, we decided to discover our own city. We walked in very old small streets, we admired splendide houses from past times, we visited museums...  There is a very beautiful church in my town, much visited by tourists. That day we had a guide just for us, so we could play some notes on the organ, we even went under the roof and it was great!</p>
            </div>
